title: Kampf um Norwegen - The Battle of Norway (1942) DVDrip
description:
<a href="http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0905617/" rel="nofollow" target="_NEW">http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0905617/</a>

Authentic German Nazi propaganda film assumed lost, found by accident at a German web auction site. Shows how the Germans occupied Norway and Denmark during WW2, opposed by British navy and Norwegian partisan forces - presented as a great victory. Genuine, original German footage from the war. Cute old-fashioned animation to explain the strategy.

Fullscreen black and white, German narrators and music, English subtitles hardcoded.

Surprisingly good quality.
XviD 544x384 25 fps, two-pass, AC3
